---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SchemaOrg from '../components/seo/SchemaOrg.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Biblioteca del Alma | Libros de Adriana Cristina Rueda Sañudo"
  description="Descubre los libros de Adriana Cristina Rueda: 'Lazos Escritos' (2023) y 'Una Voz al paso del Eclipse' (2026). Literatura para el alma y el crecimiento espiritual."
  keywords={['libros Adriana Rueda', 'Lazos Escritos', 'Una Voz al paso del Eclipse', 'literatura espiritual Colombia', 'autora colombiana']}
>
  <SchemaOrg
    slot="head"
    type={['Book']}
    data={{
      name: 'Lazos Escritos',
      genre: 'Antología',
      description: 'Colección de relatos sobre lazos humanos invisibles y conexiones del alma.',
      datePublished: '2023',
      url: 'https://adricrisrueda.com/libros',
    }}
  />
  <SchemaOrg
    slot="head"
    type={['BreadcrumbList']}
    breadcrumbs={[
      { name: 'Inicio', url: '/' },
      { name: 'Biblioteca', url: '/libros' },
    ]}
  />
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <header class="relative min-h-[70vh] flex items-center justify-center pt-24 overflow-hidden bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden pointer-events-none">
      <div class="absolute top-[-10%] right-[-10%] w-[50%] h-[60%] bg-accent/15 dark:bg-accent/10 blur-[100px] rounded-full"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-[-10%] left-[-10%] w-[45%] h-[55%] bg-secondary/15 dark:bg-secondary/10 blur-[100px] rounded-full"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10 w-full text-center">
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <span class="text-secondary tracking-[0.5em] uppercase text-xs font-semibold block">Colección Literaria</span>
        <h1 class="font-display text-6xl md:text-8xl lg:text-9xl leading-tight text-primary dark:text-white">
          Biblioteca<br/>
          <span class="italic text-accent font-light">del Alma</span>
        </h1>
        <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-secondary mx-auto rounded-full my-8"></div>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-light leading-relaxed">
          Cada libro es un peldaño en la escalera hacia la consciencia. Aquí encontrarás palabras que sanan, historias que reflejan y guías que iluminan el camino de regreso a ti.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2">
        <a class="animate-bounce p-2 text-primary dark:text-accent/70 hover:text-secondary transition-colors" href="#featured">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl">keyboard_arrow_down</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Featured Book Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-accent/10 dark:bg-accent/5 relative overflow-hidden" id="featured">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/2 h-full bg-gradient-to-l from-white/40 to-transparent dark:from-black/20 pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-16 lg:gap-24">
        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 flex justify-center lg:justify-end perspective-1000">
          <div class="relative group w-72 md:w-96">
            <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[140%] h-[140%] bg-secondary/20 dark:bg-secondary/10 blur-3xl rounded-full"></div>
            <a href="/libro" class="relative transform transition-all duration-700 hover:scale-105 hover:-rotate-2 block">
              <img
                alt="Portada de Una Voz al paso del Eclipse — guía de crecimiento espiritual por Adriana Cristina Rueda Sañudo, lanzamiento Feria del Libro de Bogotá 2026"
                class="w-full rounded-r-2xl rounded-l-md shadow-xl border-l-4 border-white/20"
                src="/images/portada-libro-2.png"
                loading="eager"
                fetchpriority="high"
                decoding="sync"
              />
              <div class="absolute -top-6 -right-6 bg-primary text-white w-24 h-24 rounded-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center shadow-lg border-4 border-white dark:border-surface-dark animate-float" style="animation-delay: 1s;">
                <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide">Nuevo</span>
                <span class="font-display font-bold text-lg">2024</span>
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full lg:w-1/2 text-center lg:text-left space-y-8">
          <div>
            <span class="inline-block py-1 px-3 rounded-full bg-accent/20 text-accent dark:text-accent font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Lanzamiento Destacado</span>
            <h2 class="font-display text-5xl md:text-6xl text-primary dark:text-white leading-tight mb-2">
              Una Voz al Paso<br/>
              <span class="italic text-secondary">del Eclipse</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-500 font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-sm">Guía de Crecimiento Espiritual</p>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 font-light text-lg leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              En la oscuridad del eclipse es donde la luz verdadera aprende a brillar. Esta obra no es solo un libro, es un compañero para esos momentos de transformación profunda donde las sombras parecen ganar terreno.
            </p>
            <p>
              A través de canalizaciones, ejercicios prácticos y poesía del alma, te invito a recorrer el camino de la incertidumbre para encontrar, del otro lado, una voz más auténtica, fuerte y tuya que nunca.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center lg:justify-start pt-4">
            <a href="/libro" class="gold-gradient hover:opacity-90 text-primary px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-display font-bold shadow-xl shadow-secondary/20 hover:shadow-secondary/40 transition-all transform hover:-translate-y-1 tracking-wide flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
              COMPRAR AHORA
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">shopping_bag</span>
            </a>
            <a href="/libro" class="bg-transparent border border-primary dark:border-gray-400 text-primary dark:text-gray-200 px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-display font-medium hover:bg-primary hover:text-white dark:hover:bg-white dark:hover:text-primary transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
              LEER PREVIEW
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">menu_book</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Quote Section -->
  <section class="py-32 bg-primary relative overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
      <svg class="w-full h-full" preserveAspectRatio="none" viewBox="0 0 100 100">
        <path d="M0 100 C 20 0 50 0 100 100 Z" fill="white"></path>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 bg-accent/20 blur-3xl rounded-full mix-blend-overlay"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-80 h-80 bg-secondary/20 blur-3xl rounded-full mix-blend-overlay"></div>
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 text-center relative z-10">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary/60 text-5xl mb-8 block">auto_stories</span>
      <blockquote class="font-display italic text-4xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl text-white leading-tight mb-8">
        "Escribir es construir puentes hacia lo invisible."
      </blockquote>
      <div class="w-16 h-0.5 bg-secondary mx-auto"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Catálogo Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark relative" id="catalogo">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-20">
        <span class="text-secondary font-bold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-xs block mb-4">Catálogo Completo</span>
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl text-primary dark:text-white">Obras Publicadas</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20">
        <!-- Libro 1: Lazos Escritos -->
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark rounded-3xl p-8 lg:p-12 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300 border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-8 items-center group">
          <div class="w-48 flex-shrink-0 perspective-1000 relative">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-secondary/20 blur-2xl rounded-full group-hover:bg-secondary/30 transition-colors"></div>
            <div class="aspect-[2/3] bg-surface-light dark:bg-gray-800 rounded shadow-lg flex items-center justify-center text-center p-4 relative z-10 transform group-hover:rotate-y-6 transition-transform duration-500 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
              <img src="/images/lazos-escritos.png" alt="Portada Lazos Escritos — antología 2023 de Adriana Cristina Rueda Sañudo" class="w-full h-full object-contain" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-grow text-center lg:text-left">
            <span class="text-secondary font-bold text-sm mb-2 block">2023 • Antología</span>
            <h3 class="font-display text-3xl text-primary dark:text-white mb-4">Lazos Escritos</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 font-light mb-6 line-clamp-3">
              Una colección de relatos que exploran las conexiones humanas invisibles. Como parte del programa "Autor de Éxito", esta obra reúne voces diversas que tejen una red de emociones compartidas y descubrimientos personales.
            </p>
            <button class="text-primary dark:text-secondary font-bold text-sm tracking-wide border-b-2 border-secondary/50 hover:border-secondary pb-1 transition-all inline-flex items-center gap-1 group-hover:gap-2">
              VER DETALLES
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base">arrow_forward</span>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Libro 2: Una Voz al Paso del Eclipse -->
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark rounded-3xl p-8 lg:p-12 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow duration-300 border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800 flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-8 items-center group">
          <div class="w-48 flex-shrink-0 perspective-1000 relative">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-accent/20 blur-2xl rounded-full group-hover:bg-accent/30 transition-colors"></div>
            <div class="aspect-[2/3] bg-surface-light dark:bg-gray-800 rounded shadow-lg flex items-center justify-center text-center p-4 relative z-10 transform group-hover:rotate-y-6 transition-transform duration-500 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
              <img src="/images/portada-libro-2.png" alt="Una Voz al paso del Eclipse — libro de crecimiento espiritual por AdriCris Rueda, 2026" class="w-full h-full object-contain" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-grow text-center lg:text-left">
            <span class="text-accent font-bold text-sm mb-2 block">2024 • Crecimiento Espiritual</span>
            <h3 class="font-display text-3xl text-primary dark:text-white mb-4 leading-tight">Una Voz al Paso del Eclipse</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 font-light mb-6 line-clamp-3">
              Una conmovedora historia de sanación y reencontrarse a uno mismo. A través de la metáfora del eclipse, este libro te invita a abrazar tu oscuridad para descubrir tu luz interior.
            </p>
            <a href="/libro" class="text-primary dark:text-secondary font-bold text-sm tracking-wide border-b-2 border-secondary/50 hover:border-secondary pb-1 transition-all inline-flex items-center gap-1 group-hover:gap-2">
              VER DETALLES
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-base">arrow_forward</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Newsletter Section -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-surface-light dark:bg-surface-dark border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary dark:text-accent text-5xl mb-6 block mx-auto animate-pulse">mark_email_unread</span>
      <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
        No te pierdas el próximo capítulo
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 font-light text-lg mb-10 max-w-lg mx-auto">
        Suscríbete para recibir noticias de nuevos lanzamientos, lecturas exclusivas y eventos literarios.
      </p>
      <form class="max-w-md mx-auto relative flex items-center">
        <div class="relative w-full">
          <div class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 pl-3 flex items-center pointer-events-none">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-gray-400">mail</span>
          </div>
          <input 
            class="block w-full pl-10 pr-32 py-4 border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 rounded-full leading-5 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 placeholder-gray-500 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-secondary focus:border-secondary sm:text-sm shadow-sm" 
            placeholder="tu@correo.com" 
            type="email"
          />
          <button 
            class="absolute inset-y-1 right-1 px-6 py-2 border border-transparent text-sm leading-5 font-bold rounded-full text-white bg-primary hover:bg-primary/90 focus:outline-none focus:bg-secondary transition duration-150 ease-in-out font-display tracking-wide" 
            type="submit"
          >
            SUSCRIBIRSE
          </button>
        </div>
      </form>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-4">Respetamos tu privacidad. Cero spam, solo esencia.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
